The room was nice and what we expected for a Holiday Inn.	The hotel is very convenient to the airport and close to Little Italy.	The bathroom in the room we stayed apeared to be updated, so that was nice.	The hotel was great.	The rooms were nice and clean.	It was close to everything.	Rooms were remodeled and it made for a good family trip.	The front desk service was very friendly.	The room itself was very clean and for a 3 star hotel had everything we needed.